  "coverage_strategy": [
    "Prioritize moving forward in clear state to cover new ground.",
    "Upon detecting an obstacle ahead, rotate in place to find a new direction.",
    "If blocked on multiple sides, initiate backward movement or full rotation to escape corners.",
    "Use wall-following (rotate toward open space when side obstacles detected) to systematically cover boundaries.",
    "Helper state 'corner_escape' prevents oscillation and deadlock in tight spaces.",
    "Never allow forward movement when obstacles are detected in front."
